descript.abstract: This polygon data layer represents parks for the City of Madison, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Madison_City_Parks_2014.gdb. Other feature classes in this geodatabase include: Botanical_Gardens, Cemeteries, Golf_Courses, Land_polygons, Mall_Concourse, Park_Name, and Zoo.
descript.purpose: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
descript.supplinf: For additional information, please see original license/data sharing agreement where applicable. The data for this layer was published with multiple feature classes, and the metadata was generated from the "Madison_City_Parks_2014" layer.
